name: Tattoo Design
description: Don’t pick something off the wall at your local tattoo shop, get something original. I will design an original tattoo for you based on your own visionary words. (All designs will be sent via email and no design can be bigger than what can fit on a 9×12 piece of paper)

name: Eyes #1
description:
Title: Eyes #1

	I decided to play with soft and hard elements in this pic. As well as using the eye as the element of focus, because the eyes can tell so much. What do these eyes tell you? What do you see?

-Soft Pastels
-Black Ink Micron Pens
-Prism Color Markers
